{"tid":191481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"種3,000萬元大麻　4人被捕","createTime":"2017-04-08T02:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T05:46:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32280dbb623406b3682b27189cc976ee208a9a03","tid":191481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19983530&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19983530%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170408&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b346ab1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19983530%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170408&h=f64f759d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19983530&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170408</a><br />\n<br />\n種3,000萬元大麻　4人被捕<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方破獲一個以高科技種植大麻的犯罪集團，前日下午搜查沙頭角4個目標場所，撿獲1,300棵大麻植物、200多克大麻草以及各類種植工具，巿值近3,000萬元，拘捕3名本地男子及一名印尼女子，包括一對兄弟。今次是警方自2007年以來搗破最大宗金額的大麻種植案。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n其中一名被捕男子昨晚被押返萊洞東村搜證。馬耀文攝<br />\n<br />\n兄弟自研種植方法<br />\n<br />\n警方調查顯示，集團以種植、烘乾及包裝的一條龍方式銷售大麻至本地巿場，各成員分工運作4個場所，他們利用強光燈及控制濕度溫度的設施，加上租用多個單位，冀以最快速方式催生大量大麻植物出售，不排除尚有涉案人士在逃。<br />\n4個大麻種植場分別位於麻雀嶺、小坑村、坪輋路、萊洞東村。被捕人士包括一對姓蘇兄弟（51歲及42歲），及一名32歲印尼女子，她為蘇弟的傭工。另一名21歲無業男子亦被捕。消息指兄長為裝修工人，弟弟則為汽車零件銷售員，兩人都有吸食大麻習慣，其後鑽研種植方法，種出高品質大麻出售。警方發現該集團的犯罪得益逾1,000萬元，包括11個戶口內合共386萬元存款、一個擁有78萬元證券的戶口、51萬元現金，以及2輛共值70萬元的私家車。<br />\n■記者馬耀文"},{"pid":"b228dae54053e8c94257fb6217346c5b5fa6c6c7","tid":191481,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"聽講話係用霧耕法...."},{"pid":"8ae9d8aee7d6fd7cbc7433f8ce2fa25fe14918d8","tid":191481,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢"},{"pid":"8a7bcdc1437b8c94e91759cfbef2518407f8f138","tid":191481,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"其實種大麻食大麻有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4678b662880756290265e3886794a5488821b30a","tid":191481,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實種大麻食大麻有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩啊 <br />\n食多d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好事黎"},{"pid":"75c4b475f6b980729f5e2183672c8db86176cea7","tid":191481,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實種大麻食大麻有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同個官講囉<br />\n係高登講有撚用"},{"pid":"f896aff62c957781621c1d19f9ae2b2278cc4f6f","tid":191481,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但有一個夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不會死 種大麻"},{"pid":"b4e18d42055cfb129087498a021c7671ca6f80d7","tid":191481,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實種大麻食大麻有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大量 同 販賣咪係問題囉....<br />\n種咁多你點同個官講係自己食?"},{"pid":"27575e0032b91d0beff23231c8ccb0c67978a67b","tid":191481,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實種大麻食大麻有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實犯法坐監有乜問題？"},{"pid":"ade505ef81e5b7c766f2d14a4fee0db102d1220c","tid":191481,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"ht